message.content:
Key Hard Skills:
1. Access control processes
2. Access catalogs management
3. Access rules definition
4. Access management processes
5. Access models optimization (e.g., Access Matrix, RBAC)
6. Compliance with company policies
7. Communication with application administrators
8. Access management tools and software (e.g., Okta)
9. Periodic reviews of access rights
10. Security protocols improvement

Key Soft Skills:
1. Problem-solving skills
2. Analytical skills
3. Communication skills
4. Team coordination
5. Compliance with internal policies
6. Attention to detail
7. Adaptability
8. Ownership and drive
9. Collaboration with stakeholders
10. Continuous learning and development
